    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center about-text-wrapper">
          <p class="about-text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">Green Saviours is a non 
            government organisation that is active in environmental conservational activities.
            They have been active since 2016.
          </p><br>
          <p class="about-text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">Large scale deforrstation
            caused by human activities, especially over the past four decades has severely impacted
            the ecological balance, caused climate change, reduction in soil fertility, large scale 
            soil erosion, depletion of water sources, increased human-animal conflict, epidemics and the
            extinction of several species of native trees, plants and animals in addition to threatening
            food and livelihood security for humans across the world.
          </p><br>
          <p class="about-text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">Urban spaces have also seen a marked
            decline in vegetation leading to the creation of Urban Heat Islands, causing extreme weather events,
            a marked increase in pollution, depletion of water tables, reducing the availibility of habitats for
            birds, insects and other species.

            <span class="about-motto">Trees for planet is our motto</span>
          </p>
